, founder of Flores Clean, at a commercial facility in the GTA","fill":true,"className":"object-cover"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0","style":{"background":"linear-gradient(to top, oklch(0.07 0 0 / 0.60) 0%, transparent 50%)"},"aria-hidden":"true"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm font-600","style":{"color":"oklch(0.92 0 0)","fontFamily":"var(--font-heading)"},"children":"Diana Flores"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs","style":{"color":"oklch(0.55 0 0)","fontFamily":"var(--font-body)"},"children":"Founder & Owner, Flores Clean"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 px-4","style":{"background":"oklch(0.09 0 0)","borderTop":"1px solid oklch(0.22 0.01 252 / 0.35)"},"children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-700 tracking-[-0.03em] mb-8","style":{"color":"oklch(0.93 0 0)","fontFamily":"var(--font-heading)"},"children":"Diana's story"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-5 text-sm leading-[1.8]","style":{"color":"oklch(0.62 0 0)","fontFamily":"var(--font-body)"},"children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Diana Flores spent the first decade of her career managing operations for a commercial property management company in York Region. In that role, she coordinated with dozens of cleaning contractors across multiple buildings — and found the same frustrations repeating: inconsistent crews, miscommunication, no single point of accountability, and cleaning companies that treated commercial accounts as an afterthought to their residential business."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"In 2019, Diana started Flores Clean with a different model in mind. Her background was in operations — not cleaning for its own sake — and she approached it as a managed service business from day one. Every client would have a dedicated account manager. Staff would be bonded and background-checked. Certifications would be maintained, not just claimed. And the company would serve commercial clients exclusively."}],"$L11","$L12"]}]]}]}],"$L13","$L14","$L15"],["$L16"],"$L17"]}]
